Carole Ashby https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carole_Ashby 0 Carole Ashby (born 24 March 1955 in Cannock, Staffordshire) is an English actress and pinup girl. She appeared as a glamour girl in the British news media during the 1970s. Carole_Ashby ( born 24_March_1955 in Cannock , Staffordshire ) is an_English_actress_and_pinup_girl .
